%S A395883 1,1,3,15,73,470,2938,19810,136048,960343,6897787,50365174,372662996
%N A395883 Number of oriented polyominoes in the {7,3} tessellation of the hyperbolic plane.
%C A395883 For oriented polyominoes, chiral pairs are counted as two.
%H A395883 <a href="https://oeis.org/wiki/PF-Non-Euclidean">Wiki page indexing sequences related to non-euclidean polyforms</a>
%F A395883 a(n) = P{p,q}(n) (the number of oriented {p,q} polyominoes of size n) is equal to P{p,oo}(n) for n <= q. In this case, P{p,oo} = A389561.
%o A395883 (C) // See A393739.
%Y A395883 Cf. A389561, A333018.
%K A395883 nonn,more,changed
